title: (PSX-PSP) Star Wars:Dark Forces converted properly (Kingdom-game
description:
STAR WARS - DARK FORCES:

The Empire is trying to create robotic soldiers known as Dark Troopers. The Rebel Alliance catches wind of this and hires Kyle Katarn to find the plans for creating and using them. You take the role of Katarn as he fights his way through 14 missions of intense action. The game is played from a first-person perspective, which puts right in the middle of the STAR WARS universe. You'll have to run, jump, crouch, and shoot your way through every nook and cranny of each stage. There will be an army of Stormtroopers, Gamorrean guards, probe droids, and other enemies on the lookout for a suspicious humanoid, so stay on your toes. Help the Rebel Alliance in its continuing fight against the Empire in STAR WARS: Dark Forces.


Tested and working properly on CFW 5.00 M33-4 combined with the 500 popsloader pack on 3.72 POPS....KloWn
